1
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:21,760
♪Evening breeze cradles verdant hills♪

2
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:27,140
♪Embracing the waves of the deep sea♪

3
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:33,670
♪Paper kites aim for distant shores♪

4
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:37,400
♪Together, we conclude our tale♪

5
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:38,520
[Land of Dreams]

6
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:41,340
[Episode 5]

7
00:00:42,660 --> 00:00:43,740
If you dare lay a finger on her,

8
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:45,100
you're dead.

9
00:00:46,620 --> 00:00:48,100
Easy, man.

10
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:51,660
I'm just a wall-jumper.

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:53,420
I don't make enemies easily.

12
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:54,780
How did you find me?

13
00:00:56,380 --> 00:01:01,500
I always climb roofs and walls
in the town.

14
00:01:01,860 --> 00:01:03,860
Finding someone is easy for me.

15
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:09,820
What do you want?

16
00:01:10,140 --> 00:01:11,700
Life is tough nowadays.

17
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:15,180
We both make our living
through our skills.

18
00:01:15,740 --> 00:01:18,380
Each has their own way.

19
00:01:19,900 --> 00:01:21,420
I just wanted to ask

20
00:01:21,780 --> 00:01:24,740
if you know any ways to make some money.

21
00:01:24,740 --> 00:01:25,740
Don't talk with that tone.

22
00:01:26,540 --> 00:01:28,540
Don't be so serious.

23
00:01:29,100 --> 00:01:30,780
I'm just inquiring

24
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:32,780
about ways to earn a living.

25
00:01:32,940 --> 00:01:34,780
I don't have any tips for you.

26
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:38,780
I'm warning you again.

27
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:41,700
If you dare come near my sister,

28
00:01:42,140 --> 00:01:43,460
you're dead.

29
00:01:59,780 --> 00:02:00,580
Thanks.

30
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:01,740
Take care.

31
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:04,780
Mengchen? What a surprise!

32
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:06,780
Any progress
about what I made you ask?

33
00:02:09,180 --> 00:02:09,980
Yes.

34
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:11,780
The person killed at the ball

35
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:13,420
was a Japanese antique dealer.

36
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,300
According to an investigation
by the Huaicheng Chamber of Commerce,

37
00:02:15,740 --> 00:02:17,620
it seems he was killed by an assassin.

38
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:19,500
But as for who did it,

39
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:20,860
that's hard to track down.

40
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:22,740
That Japanese had snatched up

41
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:24,620
a lot of antiques here,

42
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:25,580
making quite a few enemies.

43
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:28,620
Why do you want to know this?

44
00:02:30,180 --> 00:02:31,340
Just curious.

45
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:32,420
Thanks, Zeyu.

46
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:33,780
I'll be going now.

47
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,140
What happened to your arm?

48
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,260
Nothing.

49
00:02:41,740 --> 00:02:42,620
Let me take care of it.

50
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:49,660
I never expected Xiaosheng

51
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:51,300
to be an assassin.

52
00:02:52,940 --> 00:02:55,860
Who was directing him to kill Mr. Cao?

53
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:59,340
What does he have to do

54
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:01,900
with the Lin family's annihilation?

55
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:04,780
What should I do?

56
00:03:08,940 --> 00:03:09,740
Mengchen.

57
00:03:11,340 --> 00:03:12,140
Mengchen?

58
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,140
What's in your mind?

59
00:03:14,140 --> 00:03:14,940
You were so distracted.

60
00:03:16,340 --> 00:03:17,140
Nothing.

61
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:20,060
Why do you always get hurt?

62
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:22,860
Just a minor accident.

63
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,660
I'm a doctor.

64
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:25,940
You can't hide it from me.

65
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:28,940
Plus, you've always been training
martial arts, haven't you?

66
00:03:32,420 --> 00:03:33,220
Mengchen,

67
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:35,980
are you planning
to do something dangerous?

68
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,500
I don't mean to pry.

69
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,140
I just want to protect you.

70
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:44,340
Whatever you need, I'm willing to help.

71
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,300
Zeyu,

72
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,540
I need you to keep the secret for me.

73
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:51,700
No problem. I know you have your secrets,

74
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:52,860
including those about your brother.

75
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:54,820
I'll keep them.

76
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:58,740
But I really don't want you
to be in any danger.

77
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:01,420
I know.

78
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:03,100
Thank you.

79
00:04:16,420 --> 00:04:17,180
By the way,

80
00:04:17,780 --> 00:04:19,060
have you ever been to England?

81
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:22,460
I'd really love to take you there.

82
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:26,660
The Thames is especially beautiful,

83
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,820
as well as Edinburgh
perched on the cliffs,

84
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:30,660
and the majestic St. Paul's Cathedral.

85
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,420
You'll love them.

86
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:35,580
Maybe one day,

87
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:38,060
once I've sorted everything out,

88
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:40,140
I'll leave this place

89
00:04:40,380 --> 00:04:41,700
to see the world.

90
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,060
If you dare lay a finger on her,
you're dead.

91
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:13,340
Brother,

92
00:05:13,340 --> 00:05:14,580
I just remembered

93
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:17,860
Yawen asked me
to Charlie's Ballroom tonight.

94
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:22,220
Well.

95
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:24,220
I need to go back and do inventory.

96
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:46,650
[Nanyan Residence]

97
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:09,150
[Tongji Dyeing Workshop]

98
00:06:31,150 --> 00:06:33,170
[Fengchun Theater]

99
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:39,580
In the dimming desert, the sun sets west.

100
00:06:40,060 --> 00:06:45,660
Warhorses neigh, hunger in their chest.

101
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:49,260
For paths are secret, steps discreet.

102
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:52,740
The border's in sight,

103
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:55,820
no time to retreat.

104
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:59,700
Great!

105
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:01,620
Hey,

106
00:07:02,020 --> 00:07:04,060
this Yang Bajie is so popular.

107
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:07,660
Wouldn't she be recognized in her guise?

108
00:07:08,100 --> 00:07:10,060
Those who recognized her are all dead.

109
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,780
In the dimming desert, the sun sets west.

110
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:16,180
Those barbarian foes

111
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:17,940
never uncovered

112
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:21,660
I am Yang's eighth daughter

113
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:27,340
from the Song Dynasty.

114
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:30,980
Great!

115
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:55,380
♪A glance seals our fate♪

116
00:07:56,320 --> 00:08:02,180
♪Without you, time fades into night♪

117
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:08,820
♪My heart adrift,
seeking wings to break free♪

118
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:15,440
♪Through tears, our love endures♪

119
00:08:15,540 --> 00:08:18,280
♪Fate entwined♪

120
