123
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:38,740
Mengchen.

124
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:41,460
Brother, good morning.

125
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:44,340
I made you some red bean cakes.

126
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:46,140
After you finish,
I'll take you to the art school.

127
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:49,220
No need. I've made plans
to go with Yawen.

128
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:50,780
Hold on a second.

129
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:54,380
Dr. Qi came for you this morning.

130
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:55,340
I sent him away.

131
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:57,540
This is something he left for you.
Take a look.

132
00:08:58,180 --> 00:08:58,980
Zeyu?

133
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:03,540
What's this?

134
00:09:05,740 --> 00:09:06,620
A world art album.

135
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,460
It's filled

136
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:10,060
with landscapes and landmarks
from various countries.

137
00:09:10,540 --> 00:09:13,260
I told him I wanted to see the world.

138
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:14,860
So he gave me this.

139
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:18,300
You're thinking of leaving?

140
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:26,060
The world outside is vast.

141
00:09:26,420 --> 00:09:28,340
I'll go out to see it one day.

142
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:30,660
I'll see the mountains, rivers, stars,

143
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:32,220
and different cities.

144
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:33,660
I can go with you.

145
00:09:39,020 --> 00:09:39,860
Would you really leave everything behind?

146
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:40,660
I would.

147
00:09:44,460 --> 00:09:45,300
When?

148
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:52,020
Once I've settled all that needs settling.

149
00:09:53,820 --> 00:09:54,620
Alright.

150
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:58,580
Then, we'll talk again after you've

151
00:09:59,220 --> 00:10:00,220
settled everything.

152
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:02,340
♪My sorrow overwhelmed♪

153
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:06,620
♪I gaze at the moon, longing for you♪

154
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:09,500
♪Love as vast as stars♪

155
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:13,820
♪In the galaxy,
I yearn for your presence♪

156
